snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League | Season 1 - Meet the Joker
snippet.description:
Brainiac messed with the wrong clown because this Joker won’t be upstaged, not even by an Earth-shattering multiversal being. The Season 1 Free* Content Update is available now!

*Base Game required!

Buy now: https://go.wbgames.com/AvailableNow 
 
Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is available now on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.
 
Learn more: https://www.suicidesquadgame.com/en-us
